description: Critical Hit is a skill to generate Critical Hit Effects for Tabletop RPG Games with a focus on the D20 ruleset. You can get a critical hit effect by simply saying "Alexa, Critical Hit" or" Alexa, Ask Critical Hit to roll me a critical."
exampleInteractions: Tell Critical Hit to roll me a critical
name: Critical Hit
shortDescription: Critical Hit is a skill to generate Critical Hit Effects for Tabletop RPG Games
